# This directory holds runtime secrets. NEVER commit actual secret files.
#
# Expected files (generated at runtime, not in git):
#   kek.bin            — 32-byte AES-256-GCM Key Encryption Key
#                        Generated by API on first startup if missing.
#                        Mode 0600. Mounted read-only into api + worker-broker.
#
#   robinhood.pickle   — robin_stocks session token
#                        Generated interactively on host machine:
#                          python -c "import robin_stocks.robinhood as r; r.login('email', 'pass')"
#                        Copy the resulting pickle here.
#                        Mounted read-only into worker-broker.
